Overview
The Tableau Stock Performance Dashboard is a powerful data visualization tool designed to provide real-time, data-driven insights into stock market performance. This project integrates Google Sheets with Tableau to update stock data every hour, ensuring up-to-date market analysis.

Dashboard Link:
https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/sarvesh.kaushik/viz/StocksDashboard_17396707237860/StockPeformance?publish=yes

